Electron microscopy confirmed the presence of nano-sized PM in both WPS preparations (Fig. 1 b), and intact plastic smoke PM obtained by exposition of the transmission electron microscope grids to plastic smoke (Supplementary Material, Subsection 2, Fig. 2
                        ). It was revealed heterogeneity of structure of WPS particles that contained black inclusions (Fig. 1b). FTIR and Raman spectra of WPS were in Supplementary Material, Subsection 3, Fig. 3
                        .
